name: Famous Toastery
categories: Restaurants, Breakfast & Brunch, American (Traditional), Event Planning & Services, Coffee & Tea, Food, Caterers
covid_banner:
We are happy to announce that we have moved into Phase 2 (well its been a few days, but better late than never)!  We are observing all recommendations by the state and the health department to help our staff and customers stay safe!  
- All staff are required to wear masks
- All staff are required to wear gloves, and change them frequently 
- Frequent use of Sanitizer on all tables, chairs, door handles, etc
- All tables are clear of any multi use items, and we are using disposable single use items whenever possible.
- We are using recycled paper single use menus ONLY!

When you come to visit us we just ask that you don''t move any tables around, and that you do your best to maintain 6ft of distance from other customers that are not in your group!

We are happy to be able to welcome everyone back, and look forward to doing so while keeping everyone safe and comfortable!
